The Beatrice Solidwood Queen Bed features a pull out drawer and is made of kilndried and chemically treated solid Sheesham 
wood. It features an elegant headboard of 40 mm thickness, and the thickness of the footboard and side panels is 27 mm. The
 side rails are 400 mm from the floor, and it features a plywood mattress panel between them. The compatible mattress sizes
 are 78X 60 for the queen size variant and 78 X 72 for the kingsize variant. The bed has a warranty of one year against all
 kinds of manufacturing defects.

column4: With a plushly padded headrest and button tufting, this upholstered bed is as stunning as it is comfy. This bed is upholstered in durable, anti-fade fabric that will keep it looking new for years to come! Welcome to 160 litres of extra storage. Four smooth, easy-access drawers make room for all your spares. With soft cushioning and rounded corners, this bed is designed to be safe for kids (and adults alike). You can let your toddler zoom around without worrying about boo-boos!
column5: Induces yawns. In a good way. Plush and comfy, the Felicity is every insomniac’s dream come true. A gentle push turns it into an inviting single bed. Perfect for small apartments and sudden guests. Choose from 3 delectable shades. It’ll sit pretty in your living room, Made of eucalyptus wood, Foam cushioning, Fabric upholstery, The click-clack mechanism for ease of use.
column6: Lean back and relax in the tall enclosing wings of the Morgen, The comfortable wings provide plenty of head and neck support while the spacious seat lets you sit in a variety of positions, The sleek classic-contemporary lines and striking upholstery make it a great accent chair, Refer to the images for details of dimensions, For indoor use only.
column7: A minimalist marvel. The Marcel coffee table is elegant, sleek, and undeniably striking. The glossy white veneer of the table is complemented by the sheen of the metal legs. The spacious table top makes room for magazines, mugs, and more. Table top made of MDF, base made of metal, White glossy finish, Please refer to images for dimension details, For indoor use only.
column8: Blissfully Bavarian. The Bayern family's crisp, clean lines and functional details create a contemporary evolution of German modernism. The low profile tv unit sits neatly below your wall mounted flat screen. The top shelf can be pulled outwards to adjust its lenth up to nearly double its normal size. That ample surface provides plenty of room for your set top box, consoles and other electronics, Comes with two finish options – Off-white & Walnut or Off-white & Columbian Walnut.
column9: No more hang-ups. Here, there are only hang-outs with your favourite book or beverage. And the soothing to-and-fro of the Kyodo swing. So soothing, that you’ll wait for the day to end just so you can sit back, relax, and sway your way to nirvana. Frame made of aluminium with powder coating, Seat and back made of PE round rattan, Polyester cushion fabric, Materials used are water resistant, making it ideal for outdoor use.
column10: There is no spoon, you say? Look below. Two spacious drawers make room for cutlery, seasoning and placemats. Now everything’s right where you need it. We’ve also added beauty to brains with an elegant design and gorgeous finish. Made of sheesham wood with MDF drawers, Available in 2 finishes, Seats up to 4, Please refer to images for dimension details, Indoor use only.
column11: Bring dinner times back in style with the comfortable Gordon Dining Chair, Stylish angular lines are complemented by a comfortable seating posture to let you linger at the table, The sturdy wooden seat and back ensure that your dining room stays low maintenance, Made of high grade Sheesham wood, Refer to the images for details of dimensions, For indoor use only.
column12: You call it a cabinet, we call it the perfect display. The Akira features a sleek glass front, held together by warm sheesham wood. The perfect home for your museum-worthy china, it also doubles as a serving station. Made from sheesham wood and glass, with acacia wood shelves, Available in 2 finishes, Available in 2 sizes, Indoor use only.
column13: A shot for every time someone asks “Where’d you get this from?” A mirrored back panel, and sleek legs and handles make the Boisdale a conversation starter. A laddered shelf lets you spot bottles with ease. An overhead rack keeps wine glasses safe. Pull open a drawer and voila! It’s also a mixing counter. Made of mango wood in a dark walnut finish, Mirrored interior panel, Storage capacity: 12 bottles (approx.) | 9 whiskey glasses + 9 tall glasses | 6 wine glasses, MDF back panel.
column14: Large folding bookshelf with 5 spacious shelves, Slatted frame and shelves with a simple style that blends into most décor, Can be used as a bookshelf, decorative display or room divider, Made of high-grade Sheesham wood, Removable shelves allow you to configure the interior space as you require, Whole bookshelf can be folded to a flat package for transport or storage, Dimensions: 24 inches by 13 inches with a 65 inch height split evenly among 5 shelves, Indoor use only.
column15: An icon in every sense of the word. The Lounge Chair & Ottoman (1956) designed by Charles E. and Ray E., is considered to be one of the most significant designs of the 20th century, This high quality replica pairs sleek moulded plywood with soft artificial leather to create an inviting form that's both beautiful and supremely comfortable, The chair and ottoman are both mounted on swivelling metal bases, For indoor use only.
column16: Flexi-time. The Niccol adjustable study table is best suited to today’s students and workaholics, as its flexible design option offers several configurations. Simply swivel its table or desk on its smooth castor wheels, to make the most of corners or  long, narrow spaces. A mix of open and closed storage offers plenty of room to store books, files, stationery and more. And should a pathbreaking idea happen to strike as you work, simply jot it down on its glass tabletop that doubles as a whiteboard. Desk made from engineered wood (MDF), Table made of powder-coated metal, with a 8mm toughened glass tabletop.
column17: Meshed up. The Venturi study chair understands your back, and neck. The double mesh back is designed for comfort and support. The curved seat and back are additional ergonomic features to ensure that your working day sails smoothly ahead. Adjustable seat height, head rest height & angle and free rolling castors make it practical as well as stylish, Available in a choice of 3 colours - Aqua, Coffee, and Ash Grey, For indoor use only.
